{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb8579f15-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s5336"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5336"},"text":"§ 5336.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Additional step-increases","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb8579f16-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s5336/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Within the limit of available appropriations and under regulations prescribed by the Office of Personnel Management, the head of each agency may grant additional step-increases in recognition of high quality performance above that ordinarily found in the type of position concerned. However, an employee is eligible under this section for only one additional step-increase within any 52-week period.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb8579f17-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s5336/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A step-increase under this section is in addition to those under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t5/s5335"},"text":"section 5335 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and is not an equivalent increase in pay within the meaning of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t5/s5335/a"},"text":"section 5335(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb8579f18-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s5336/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" This section does not apply to the pay of an individual appointed by the President, by and with the advice and consent of the Senate.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idb8579f19-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/554"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–554","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1966-09-06"},"text":"Sept. 6, 1966","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/80/469"},"text":"80 Stat. 469","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/454/tV/s503/h"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–454, title V, § 503(h)","children":[],"tail":", title IX, § 906(a)(2), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-10-13"},"text":"Oct. 13, 1978","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/92/1184"},"text":"92 Stat. 1184","children":[],"tail":", 1224; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/615/tII/s204/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–615, title II, § 204(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1984-11-08"},"text":"Nov. 8, 1984","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/98/3216"},"text":"98 Stat. 3216","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/89/s3/b/1/I"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–89, § 3(b)(1)(I)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-09-30"},"text":"Sept. 30, 1993","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/107/982"},"text":"107 Stat. 982","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idb8579f1a-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"historicalAndRevision","id":"idb8579f1b-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:table","attrib":{"width":"50%","id":"idb8579f1c-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:colgroup","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:col","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"html:col","attrib":{},"text":null,"ch